{
  "stem": "26465.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He put my grandmother, who was the matriarch, he just pushed her aside, and he treated us worse than dogs.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we had to, for example-- one of the examples, we were, of course, most of the time walking barefoot.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was already November-- very-- quite cold at the time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Some ice was there on the river.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there was this big tree, for example, that fell into the water after the storm.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he-- he was asking us to go into that water and help him to cut the branches.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we did that barefoot and in frigid water.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And when we couldn't take it anymore, he asked us to go up on the landing and run until our feet-- feet would regain their heat.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we're going back and forth like that all day, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "One of the examples-- and he just couldn't wait to send us to Germany, when he heard that people are going to be taken to Germany.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And of course I, myself, I thought, if I go to Germany, that's not too far to go to France.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I'll go to France.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I'll find my parents, and everything will be fine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not the specific people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was-- mostly-- most people were-- there were 10 people chosen from our community.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I know about three people I remember.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- but Helen was the most-- she came with me, I believe.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I had no idea, no idea whatsoever, why we were sort of-- chosen to go.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, well, before I went, I believe I must have told you, in Sieniawa, they was-- they were forming a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were working, as a matter of fact, in the fields with my brother and my aunts.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
